javadoc: Array of longs that grows as needed.

methods.name: put
methods.comment:
Puts the given long value in the long array at
 the given index

methods.name: remove
methods.comment: Sets the value at the given index to 0.

methods.name: get
methods.comment: Returns the long at the given index

return.comment:
The long value at the given index. A 0 will
 be returned for any index not initialized to
 another value.
